{"color":"DEFAULT","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":false,"isArchived":false,"textContent":"\"It was correct that I be alive\" I wanted to feel it.\nOnly to confirm this, I walked all the way from Hiroshima\nSuffer became words, sorrow became anger,\nI have walked all the way here with a broken body.\nEven if I close my ears, there is a shriek that can be heard\nEven though I close my heart, there is a full of love that can be felt\nFlap, folded paper cranes, from me to you\n\n\n2\nI'm glad to be alive, I wanted to find it\nFrom the town of Nagasaki I have walked\nI have walked here from the town of Nagasaki, wanting to find it\nI have walked here from under the burnt ruins\nEven if this ear is closed, there is a voice to be heard\nEven if this heart is closed, there is abundant love\nFlap, folded paper cranes, from me to you\nFolded paper cranes, from you to the world","title":"Orizuru","userEditedTimestampUsec":1666712950246000,"createdTimestampUsec":1666712939641000,"textContentHtml":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&quot;It was correct that I be alive&quot; I wanted to feel it.<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Only to confirm this, I walked all the way from Hiroshima<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;fon